_sText: This is a Gun Game Map in the Location from a old German Farm House. There are 2 Sideways and a little Wood House into the Center. You can go trough the Wooden House. I have all symetric build on the Map, i think its better for the fair Gameplay. I have the Hammer Files put in the Pack, so you can costum the Map. Enjoy and have fun. If somebody put my Map on his Server, plz tell me this, i like to play my Map online with other People.
